@startuml getCurrentState
title 顺序图 - getCurrentState() 系统状态快照

actor 用户 as User
participant "边界层\nApiController" as API
participant "控制层\nSimulationService" as Sim
participant "控制层\nBillingEngine" as BillEng
participant "仓库层\nChargingPileRepository" as CPR
participant "仓库层\nQueueRecordRepository" as QRR
participant "仓库层\nVehicleRepository" as VR
participant "仓库层\nBillRepository" as BR
participant "仓库层\nDetailListRepository" as DLR
participant "仓库层\nRechargeRecordRepository" as RRR

User -> API : GET /api/state

API -> Sim : getCurrentTimeStr()
Sim --> API : "HH:mm:ss"
API -> Sim : getCurrentSec()
Sim --> API : int (秒)
API -> Sim : getEventTemplates()
Sim --> API : List<SimEventTemplate>

API -> CPR : findAll()
CPR --> API : List<ChargingPile>

API -> QRR : findAll()
QRR --> API : List<QueueRecord>
API -> API : 按 queueType 分类组装\nwaitingArea / faultQueue / pileQueues

API -> VR : findAll()
VR --> API : List<Vehicle>

API -> BR : findAll()
BR --> API : List<Bill>

API -> DLR : findAll()
DLR --> API : List<DetailList>

loop 每个车辆 (buildVehicleProgressMap)
    API -> RRR : findByVehicleId(vehicleId)
    RRR --> API : List<RechargeRecord>
    API -> BillEng : calculate(startTime, simNow, chargedAmount)
    BillEng --> API : BillingResult (totalCost)
end

API -> API : 组装 Map<String, Object>\n(time, piles, waitingArea, faultQueue,\n pileQueues, vehicles, bills, details,\n events, vehicleProgress, ...)

API --> User : 200 OK + 系统状态 JSON
@enduml